Chương 2. Biến ngẫu nhiên¶

$\hspace{9cm}$ PGS.TS. L Xun Trng

Ni dung

  • Khi nim v bin ngu nhin

  • Phn phi xc sut ca bin ngu nhin

    • Hm phn phi xc sut tch ly

    • Bng phn phi xc sut ca bin ngu nhin ri rc

    • Hm mt xc sut ca bin ngu nhin lin tc

  • Mt s c trng ca bin ngu nhin

    • K vng

    • Phng sai

    • Mode v trung v

  • Cc phn phi xc sut quan trng

Khái niệm biến ngẫu nhiên¶

Gi s $\Omega$ l mt khng gian mu ca mt th nghim ngu nhin.

nh ngha 1 $\,\,$ Mi hm s $X : \Omega \to \mathbb{R}$ c gi l bin ngu nhin trn $\Omega$.

  • Bin ngu nhin ri rc: $\,\,$ tp gi tr ca $X$ l mt tp hu hn hoc m c

  • Bin ngu nhin lin tc: $\,\,$ tp gi tr ca $X$ l mt tp v hn khng m c

V d 1

Trong mt ci ti c 1 bi v 99 bi en. Ngi chi cn b ra 10000 ng ly ngu nhin 1 bi. Nu ly trng bi th c thng 100000 ng. Nu ly trng bi en th khng c thng. Gi $X$ l s tin m ngi chi c sau 1 ln ly bi. Khi $X$ l mt bin ngu nhin ri rc nhn cc gi tr 90000 v -10000.

V d 2

Trong mt tr chi, ngi chi tung mt ng xu. Nu xut hin mt sp th ngi c mt ng, xut hin mt nga th mt mt ng. Gi $X$ l s tin ngi chi c c sau $n$ ln chi. Khi $X$ l mt bin ngu nhin ri rc, nhn cc gi tr nguyn trong khong $[-n, n]$.

V d 3 $\,\,$ Gi $Y$ l nhit trong mt ngy. Khi $Y$ l mt s ngu nhin lin tc nhn gi tr t $-90^oC$ n $71^oC.$

(Nm 1983, nhit thp k lc tng c ghi nhn ti trm Vostok l $-89,2^oC.$ Sa mc Lut ti Iran l vng t nng nht trn Tri t vi nhit ln ti $70,7^o C$ vo nm 2005)

Phân phối xác suất của biến ngẫu nhiên¶

nh ngha 2 $\,\,$ Cho $\Omega$ l khng gian mu ca mt th nghim ngu nhin v $P$ l o xc sut trn $\Omega$. Nu $X$ l mt bin ngu nhin trn $\Omega$ th hm s $$ F : \mathbb{R} \to [0, 1] $$ $$ F_X(x) = P(\{\omega \in \Omega \,:\, X(\omega) \leq x\}), \,x \in \mathbb{R} ,$$ c gi l hm phn phi xc sut tch ly ca bin ngu nhin $X$.

Ch 1 $\,\,$ Ta c th thy rng hm phn phi xc sut tch ly $F_X$ c cc tnh cht sau

  • $F_X$ l hm khng gim

  • $F_X(-\infty) = 0$ v $F_X(\infty) = 1$

nh ngha 3 (Bng phn phi xc sut ca bin ngu nhin ri rc) $\,\,$ Cho $X$ l mt bin ngu nhin ri rc trn khng gian mu $\Omega$ vi tp gi tr $$ \{x_1, x_2, ..., x_k, \ldots\} $$ Bng c xc nh nh di y, trong $p_k = P(X = x_k)$, c gi l bng phn phi xc sut ca $X$:

$X$ $x_1$ $x_2$ $\cdots$ $x_k$ $\cdots$
$P(X = x_k)$ $p_1$ $p_2$ $\cdots$ $p_k$ $\cdots$

Ch 2 $\,\,$ T cc nh ngha trn ta c th suy ra mi lin h gia hm phn phi xc sut tch ly v bng phn phi xc sut ca bin ngu nhin ri rc. C th nh sau

  • Hm phn phi xc sut tch ly c th c xc nh t bng phn phi xc sut $$ F_X(x) = \sum\limits_{i=1}^n p_i \quad \text{nu} \,\, x_{n-1} \leq x < x_n $$
  • Ngc li ta c $\,\, p_i = F(x_i) - F(x_{i-1})$

V d 4 $\,\,$ Gi $X$ l s chm xut hin khi tung xc sc. Xc nh bng phn phi xc sut v hm phn phi xc sut tch ly ca $X$.

V d 5 $\,\,$ Mt x th ch c 3 vin n. Anh ta c yu cu bn tng pht cho n khi trng mc tiu th dng bn, bit rng xc sut trng ca mi ln bn l 0,6. Hy lp bng phn phi xc sut v hm phn phi xc sut tch ly ca s n cn bn.

V d 6 $\,\,$ Gieo mt con xc xc v gi $X$ l s ln gieo n khi gp mt 6 chm. Lp bng phn phi xc sut ca $X$.

V d 7 $\,\,$ C hai l hng: l 1 c 10 sn phm trong c 3 sn phm loi A; l 2 c 12 sn phm trong c 4 sn phm loi A.

  • Ly ngu nhin mi l mt sn phm. Gi $X$ l s sn phm loi A ly c. Lp bng phn phi xc sut ca $X$
  • Chn ngu nhin mt l hng, t ly ngu nhin 3 sn phm. t $Y$ l s sn phm loi A ly c. Lp bng phn phi xc sut ca $Y$.
$$ P(X = 0) = \frac{C^1_{7}}{C^1_{10}}.\frac{C^1_{8}}{C^1_{12}} = \frac{7}{15}, \quad P(X = 1) = \frac{C^1_{3}}{C^1_{10}}.\frac{C^1_{8}}{C^1_{12}} + \frac{C^1_{7}}{C^1_{10}}.\frac{C^1_{4}}{C^1_{12}} = \frac{13}{30}, \quad P(X = 2) = \frac{C^1_{3}}{C^1_{10}}.\frac{C^1_{4}}{C^1_{12}} = \frac{1}{10} $$

nh nga 3 (Hm mt xc sut ca bin ngu nhin lin tc) $\,\,$ Cho $X$ l mt bin ngu nhin lin tc trn khng gian mu $\Omega$. Mt hm s $f_X$ tha cc tnh cht sau

  • $f_X(x) \geq 0$

  • $\displaystyle \int_{-\infty}^\infty f_X(x)dx = 1$

  • $P(a \leq X \leq b) = \displaystyle \int_a^b f_X(x)dx$

c gi l hm mt xc sut ca bin ngu nhin $X$.

$\hspace{7cm}$

Ch 3 $\,\,$ Tng t trng hp bin ngu nhin ri rc, c mi lin h gia hm mt xc sut v hm phn phi xc sut tch ly ca bin ngu nhin $X$ nh sau

  • Vi mi $x \in \mathbb{R}$ ta c $F_X(x) = \displaystyle \int_{-\infty}^x f_X(y)dy$

  • Nu $F_X$ l hm s kh vi, ta c $f_X(x) = F_X'(x)$

Ch 4 $\,\,$ Nu $X$ l mt bin ngu nhin lin tc vi hm mt l $f_X$ th ta c $P(X = a) = \displaystyle \int_a^a f_X(x)dx = 0$.

V d 8 $\,\,$ Thi gian s dng ca mt thit b in t (tnh bng nm) l mt bin ngu nhin lin $X$ c hm mt $$ f_X(x) = \begin{cases} kx^{-3} & \text{nu} \,\, x \geq 1, \\ 0 & \text{nu} \,\, x < 1. \end{cases} $$

  • Tm hm phn phi xc sut tch ly ca $X$
  • Tnh xc sut thit b s dng c hn 5 nm

V d 9 $\,\,$ Thi gian phc v mi khch hng ti mt ca hng l mt bin ngu nhin lin tc $X$ (tnh bng pht) c hm mt xc sut nh sau $$ f_X(x) = \begin{cases} ke^{-4x} & \text{nu} \,\, x > 0, \\ 0 & \text{nu} \,\, x \leq 0. \end{cases} $$

  • Tm hm phn phi xc sut tch ly ca $X$
  • Tnh xc sut thi gian phc v mt khch hng trong khong thi gian t 1 n 2 pht

V d 10 $\,\,$ Gi $X$ l thi gian s dng ca mt loi pin (tnh bng nm). Gi s hm mt xc sut ca $X$ c cho bi $$ f_X(x) = \begin{cases} 0,5e^{-0,5x} & \text{nu} \,\, x > 0, \\ 0 & \text{nu} \,\, x \leq 0. \end{cases} $$

  • Tnh xc sut loi pin ny s dng c t hn 2 nm hoc nhiu hn 4 nm
  • Gi s c mt vin pin loi ny c s dng 2 nm. Tnh xc sut pin ny c s dng t nht 3 nm.

V d 11 $\,\,$ Gi $X$ l thi gian (thng) s dng ca mt loi thit b in t. Gi s bin ngu nhin $X$ c hm phn phi xc sut tch ly $$ F_X(x) = \begin{cases} 1- e^{-0,03x^{1,2}} & \text{nu} \,\, x > 0, \\ 0 & \text{nu} \,\, x \leq 0. \end{cases} $$

  • Chn ngu nhin mt thit b. Tnh xc sut thit b s dng c t nht 12 thng.
  • Tm hm mt xc sut ca $X$

Một số đặc trưng của biến ngẫu nhiên¶

nh ngha 4 $\,\,$ K vng (Expected) ca mt bin ngu nhin $X$ l mt s c xc nh nh sau

  • Nu $X$ l ri rc vi tp gi tr $\{x_1, x_2, \ldots\}$ th $$ \mu_X \equiv E(X) := \sum\limits_{i\geq 1}x_iP(X = x_i) $$
  • Nu $X$ l lin tc vi hm mt xc sut l $f_X$ th $$ \mu_X \equiv E(X) := \int_{-\infty}^\infty xf_X(x)dx $$

Ch 5 $\,\,$ K vng ca bin ngu nhin l gi tr trung bnh c trng s ca tt cc cc gi tr ca bin ngu nhin .

nh ngha 5 $\,\,$ Phng sai (Variance) ca mt bin ngu nhin $X$ l i lng o lng s phn tn ca bin ngu nhin so vi gi tr k vng, v c xc nh nh sau

  • Nu $X$ l ri rc vi tp gi tr $\{x_1, x_2, \ldots\}$ th $$ \sigma_X^2 \equiv Var(X) := E[(X - \mu_X)^2] = \sum\limits_{i\geq 1}(x_i -\mu_X)^2P(X_i = x_i) $$
  • Nu $X$ l lin tc vi hm mt xc sut l $f_X$ th $$ \sigma_X^2 \equiv Var(X) := E[(X - \mu_X)^2] = \int_{-\infty}^\infty (x - \mu_X)^2f_X(x)dx $$

Ch 6 $\,\,$ Cn bc hai ca phng sai c gi l lch chun (standard deviation) ca bin ngu nhin

nh ngha 6 $\,\,$ Mode ca mt bin ngu nhin $X$ l mt s thc $\alpha$ sao cho

  • $P(X = \alpha) = \max\{P(X = x_i) \,:\, i = 1, 2, \ldots\}$ trong trng hp $X$ l ri rc vi tp gi tr l $\{x_1, x_2, \ldots\}$

  • $f_X(\alpha) = \max \{f_X(x) \,:\, x \in \mathbb{R}\}$ nu $X$ l bin ngu nhin lin tc vi hm mt xc sut $f_X$

V d 12 $\,\,$ Trong mt hp c $99$ tm th en v $1$ tm th . Mi ln rt th ngi chi s phi tr $1000$ ng. Nu rt trng th mu th ngi chi c thng $100000$ ng. Gi $X_n$ l s tin ngi chi t c sau $n$ ln rt (sau mi ln rt tm th c b li vo trong hp).

  • Tnh $E(X_1)$, $Var(X_1)$ v Mod($X_1$)

  • Tnh $E(X_2)$, $Var(X_2)$ v Mod($X_2$)

V d 13 $\,\,$ Gi $X$ l khi lng ct (tnh bng tn) do mt cng ty bn ra hng tun. Gi s bin ngu nhin $X$ c hm mt xc sut nh sau $$ f_X(x) = \begin{cases} 1,5(1- x^2) & \text{nu} \,\, 0 \leq x \leq 1, \\ 0 & \text{nu} \,\, x \notin [0, 1]. \end{cases} $$ Tnh k vng v phng sai ca $X$ v Mod($X$)

nh l 1 $\,\,$ Cho $X$ l mt bin ngu nhin v $a, b \in \mathbb{R}$. Khi

  • $E(aX + b) = aE(x) + b$

  • $Var(aX + b) = a^2Var(x)$

  • $Var(X) = E(X^2) - (E(X))^2$

nh l 2 $\,\,$ Gi s $X$ l mt bin ngu nhin v $g: \mathbb{R} \to \mathbb{R}$ l mt hm s. Khi

  • Nu $X$ l ri rc th $$ E[g(X)] = \sum\limits_{x}g(x)P(X = x) $$
  • Nu $X$ l lin tc vi hm mt xc sut $f_X$ th $$ E[g(X)] = \int_{-\infty}^\infty g(x)f_X(x)dx $$

V d 14 $\,\,$ Mt trung tm bo hnh laptop thy rng s laptop hiu Potpal cn sa trong nm ti a l 3 my. Cho $X$ l s latop Potpal cn sa trong mt nm. Da trn cc s liu c, bng phn phi xc sut ca $X$ nh sau $\hspace{5cm}$
| X | 0 | 1 | 2 | 3 | |----------|-----|-----|-----|-----| | P(X = x) | 0,2 | 0,3 | 0,4 | 0,1 |

  • Trong mt nm, trung bnh c bao nhiu laptop Potpal cn sa?

  • Tm phng sai, lch chun v mode ca $X$

  • Mt ca hng $Z$ c hp ng vi trung tm bo hnh i vi vic sa laptop Potpal nh sau: Ph dch v c nh hng nm l $200\$$ v thm $50\$$ cho mi laptop c sa. Tm trung bnh, phng sai v lch chun ca s tin m ca hng $Z$ tr cho trung tm bo hnh mi nm.

V d 15 $\,\,$ Mt ca hng bn mt loi ha cht thy rng lng ha cht bn ra hng tun (n v tnh l trm lt) c hm mt xc sut l $$ f_X(x) = \begin{cases} \displaystyle \frac{x}{2} & \text{nu} \,\, 0 \leq x \leq 2, \\ 0 & \text{cc trng hp khc}. \end{cases} $$ Gi s mi tun, chi ph bo dng ca hng l 50$. Ca hng mua mi lt ha cht l $1,75\$$ v bn ra $2,7\$$.

  • Tnh lng ha cht trung bnh bn ra hng tun

  • Tnh li nhun trung bnh hng tun ca ca hng

  • Tnh mode ca $X$

nh l 3 (nh l Chebyshev) $\,\,$ Cho $X$ l bin ngu nhin c k vng l $\mu_X$ v phng sai $\sigma^2_X$. Khi , vi mi $\epsilon > 0$, ta c $$ P(|X - \mu_X| > \epsilon) \leq \frac{\sigma^2}{\epsilon^2}. $$

Ch 7 $\,\,$ nh l Chebyshev cho thy rng $$ P(\mu_X - \epsilon \leq X \leq \mu_X + \epsilon) \geq 1 - \frac{\sigma^2}{\epsilon^2}. $$

$\hspace{5cm}$

V d 16 $\,\,$ Kho st tnh hnh sn xut trong nm 2021, gim c mt nh my thy rng trung bnh mt ngy lm c $120$ sn phm vi lch chun l $10$.

  • T l nhng ngy nh my sn xut c t 100 n 140 sn phm c nhiu hn $70\%$ khng?

  • Tm khong s lng sn phm ngn nht cha t nht $90\%$ mc sn xut hng ngy.

nh ngha 7 (Trung v) $\,\,$ Trung v (Median) ca mt bin ngu nhin $X$ l gi tr $\alpha \in \mathbb{R}$ sao cho $$ P(X \leq \alpha) = P(X \geq \alpha). $$ Ta k hiu $\alpha = Med(X)$.

Ch 8 $\,\,$ Nu $X$ l bin ngu nhin ri rc vi tp gi tr $\{x_1, x_2, \ldots\}$ th $Med(X) = x_k$ nu $$ F_X(x_{k-1}) < 0,5 \leq F_X(x_k). $$ Nu $X$ l bin ngu nhin lin tc vi hm mt l $f_X$ th $Med(X) = \alpha$ nu $$ \int_{-\infty}^\alpha f_X(x)dx = 0,5. $$

Các phân phối xác suất quan trọng¶

C mt s phn phi xc sut xut hin thng xuyn trong cc ng dng thc t. Mc ny dnh cho vic trnh by nhng tnh cht c bn nht ca vi phn phi nh nh vy. Chng ta s tp trung vo cc phn phi sau

  • Cc phn phi ri rc: phn phi Bernoulli

  • Phn phi nh thc

  • Phn phi siu bi

  • Phn phi Poisson

  • Phn phi chun

  • Phn phi $\Chi^2$

  • Phn phi Student

  • Phn phi Fisher

Phân phối Bernoulli (Bernoulli's distribution)¶

  • Mt php th ngu nhin vi khng gian mu gm hai phn t c gi l php th Bernoulli.

  • Ta ni mt bin ngu nhin $X$ c phn phi Bernoulli vi tham s $p$ nu $X$ ch nhn hai gi tr l $0$ v $1$. Ngoi ra $$ P(X = 1) = p \quad \text{v} \quad P(X = 0) = 1-p. $$ $\qquad$ Trong trng hp ny ta k hiu $X \sim B(p)$.

  • Nu $X \sim B(p)$ th ta c $\,\, E(X) = p$ v $Var(X) = p(1-p)$.

V d 17 $\,\,$ Mt cu hi trc nghim c 4 phng n tr li trong c mt phng n ng. Mt sinh vin chn ngu nhin mt phng n tr li cu hi . Nu tr li ng, sinh vin c $1$ im, nu tr li sai sinh vin c $0$ im. Gi A l bin c "sinh vin chn phng n ng".

  • Vic tr li ca sinh vin c xem l mt php th Bernoulli vi khng gian mu l $\Omega = \{A, \overline{A}\}$ v $$ P(A) = \frac{1}{4} \quad \text{v} \quad P(\overline{A}) = \frac{3}{4}. $$
  • Goi $X$ l s im ca sinh vin sau khi tr li. Khi bng phn phi xc sut ca $X$ c xc nh bi $$ P(X=1) = P(A) = \frac{1}{4} \quad \text{v} \quad P(X=0) = P(\overline{A}) = \frac{3}{4}. $$ $\qquad$ Do $X$ l mt bin ngu nhin c phn phi Bernoulli vi tham s l $0,25$ ($X \sim B(0,25)$)

Phân phối nhị thức (Binomial distribution)¶

  • Cho $p \in (0, 1)$ v $X$ l mt bin ngu nhin ri rc vi tp gi tr l $$ \{0, 1, \ldots, n\}, $$ $\qquad$ trong $n \in \mathbb{N}$. Nu phn phi xc sut ca $X$ c xc nh bi $$ p_k = P(X = k) = C_n^kp^k(1-p)^{n-k}, \,\, k = 0, 1,\ldots, n, $$ $\qquad$ th ta ni $X$ c phn phi nh thc vi hai tham s $n$ v $p$, k hiu $X \sim B(n,p)$.

  • Mt tnh hung quan trng thng gp dn n vic xut hin bin ngu nhin c phn phi nh thc c m t nh sau:

    • C $n$ php th ngu nhin c thc hin

    • Mi php th ch c th c hai kh nng xy ra l thng (bin c $A$) hoc thua (bin c $\overline{A}$)

    • Xc sut thng lun l $P(A) = p \in (0, 1)$

    • Kt qu ca mi php th l c lp vi tt c cc php th khc

    • Ta quan tm n bin ngu nhin $X$, s ln thng trong $n$ php th c thc hin. Khi $X \sim B(n, p)$.

V d 18 $\,\,$ Trong phn xng c 5 my hot ng c lp. Xc sut trong mi ca mi my b hng u bng 0,1.

  • Tm xc sut trong ca c ng 2 my hng.

  • Bit rng trong mt ca c ng 2 my hng. Tnh xc sut my th nht khng hng.

nh l 4 $\,\,$ Cho $X$ l bin ngu nhin c phn phi nh thc vi hai tham s l $n$ v $p$. Khi

  • $E(X) = np$ v $Var(X) = np(1-p)$

  • Nu $(n+1)p$ l s nguyn th $Mod(X) = (n+1)p-1$ hoc $Mod(X) = (n+1)p$.

  • Nu $(n+1)p$ l khng l s nguyn th $Mod(X) = [(n+1)p]$ (Phn nguyn ca $(n+1)p$)

Chng minh (cng thc xc nh Mode) $\,\,$ Ta c $X \sim B(n, p)$ nn $$ P(X = k) = C_n^kp^k(1-p)^{n-k}. $$ Vi $k = 0, 1, \ldots, n-1$, ta c $$ \frac{P(X = k+1)}{P(X=k)} = \frac{C_n^{k+1}p^{k+1}(1-p)^{n-k-1}}{C_n^kp^k(1-p)^{n-k}} = \frac{n-k}{k+1}.\frac{p}{1-p} = 1 + \frac{(n+1)p-1-k}{(k+1)(1-p)}. $$ Trng hp $(n+1)p = m + f$ vi $m$ l s nguyn v $0 < f < 1$. Khi $$ \frac{P(X = k+1)}{P(X=k)} = 1 + \frac{m+f - (k+1)}{(k+1)(1-p)}. $$ T y suy ra $$ \frac{P(X = k+1)}{P(X=k)} > 1 \quad \text{vi mi $k = 0, 1, \ldots, m - 1$} $$ $$ \frac{P(X = k+1)}{P(X=k)} < 1 \quad \text{vi mi $k = m, m+1, \ldots, n-1$}. $$ Do $$ \frac{P(X = 1)}{P(X=0)} > 1, \frac{P(X = 2)}{P(X=1)} > 1, \ldots, \frac{P(X = m)}{P(X=m-1)} > 1 $$ $$ \frac{P(X = m+1)}{P(X=m)} < 1, \frac{P(X = m+2)}{P(X=m+1)} < 1, \ldots, \frac{P(X = n)}{P(X=n-1)} < 1 $$ Cc bt ng thc ny chng t $Mod(X) = [(n+1)p]$. Trng hp $(n+1)p$ l s nguyn th chng minh tng t.

V d 19 $\,\,$ T l mc Covid-19 mt thnh ph n l 10%. Trong t khm bnh cho vng , ngi ta khm 100 ngi.

  • Tm s ngi b Covid-19 c kh nng xy ra nht? Tnh xc sut tng ng.

Li gii $\,\,$ Gi $X$ l s ngi b Covid-19 trong 100 ngi c thm khm. Khi $X \sim B(100; 0,1)$. Theo nh l 4 ta c $$ Mod(X) = [np + p] = 10 $$ iu ny c ngha l kh nng cao nht c $10$ ngi b Covid-19. Xc sut iu ny xy ra l $P(X=10) = C_{100}^{10}(0,1)^10(0,9)^{90} \approx 0,1319$.

Phân phối siêu bội (Hypergeometric distribution)¶

  • Xt mt tp c $N$ phn t trong c $M$ phn t c tnh cht $\mathcal{P}$ v $N-M$ phn t khng c tnh cht $\mathcal{P}$

  • Chn ngu nhin $n$ phn t t $N$ phn t ca tp hp .

  • Gi $X$ l s phn t c tnh cht $\mathcal{P}$ trong $n$ phn t chn. Khi $$ P(X = k) = \frac{C_M^kC_{N-M}^{n-k}}{C_N^n}, \,\, 0 \leq k \leq n. $$ $\qquad$ Ta ni $X$ c phn phi siu bi vi ba tham s $N, M, n$. K hiu $X \sim H(N, M, n)$.

nh l 5 $\,\,$ Nu $X$ l bin ngu nhin c phn phi siu bi $H(N, M, n)$ th k vng v phng sai ca $X$ c xc nh bi $$ E(X) = n\frac{M}{N} \quad \text{v} \quad Var(X) = \frac{nM}{N}\frac{N-n}{N-1}\Big(1-\frac{M}{N}\Big) $$

V d 20 $\,\,$ Mt cng ty nhn c mu cho hng t 20 nh cung cp my in, trong c 8 n v cung cp my in HP v 12 n v cung cp my in Canon. Chn ngu nhin $5$ mu cho hng. Tnh xc sut trong $5$ mu cho hng c $3$ mu my in Canon.

V d 21 $\,\,$ Trong $100$ laptop trng by ti ca hng POTPAL c $70$ laptop hiu LG. Chn ngu nhin $40$ laptop trong s $100$ laptop. Gi $X$ l s laptop hiu LG trong s $40$ laptop c chn.

  • Tnh xc sut chn c t $27$ n $29$ laptop LG

  • Tnh $E(X)$ v $Var(X)$

Phân phối Poisson (Poisson's distribution)¶

nh ngha $\,\,$ Cho $\lambda$ l mt s dng v $X$ l mt bin ngu nhin ri rc vi tp gi tr $$ \{0, 1, 2, \ldots, \}. $$ $\qquad$ Nu phn phi xc sut ca $X$ c xc nh bi $$ p_k = P(X = k) = e^{-\lambda}\frac{\lambda^k}{k!}, \quad k = 0, 1, 2, \ldots $$ $\qquad$ th ta ni $X$ c phn phi Poisson vi tham s $\lambda$, k hiu $X \sim Poi(\lambda)$.

Phn phi Poisson thng xut hin trong nhng tnh hung c c im sau: $\,$

Khi ta quan st mt s kin trong mt khong thi gian (hoc khng gian) vi kch thc $t$. Gi $\mu$ l tn s xy ra s kin (s ln s kin xy ra/n v thi gian) v $X$ l tng s ln s kin xy ra trong khong thi gian hoc khng gian . Nu cc gi thit sau tho mn:

  • S ln s kin xut hin trong mt khong thi gian (hoc khng gian) bt k l c lp vi s ln s kin y xut hin trong khong thi gian (hoc khng gian) khc, khng c phn giao vi khong thi gian (hoc khng gian) kia.

  • Phn b ca s ln s kin xy ra trong cc khong thi gian (hoc khng gian) l nh nhau, i vi tt c cc khong thi gian (hoc khng gian) c cng kch thc.

  • Trn cc khong thi gian (hoc khng gian) c kch thc nh, xc sut s kin xy ra l t l vi kch thc khong thi gian (hoc khng gian).

  • Xc sut s kin xy ra s dn n khng khi khong thi gian (hoc khng gian) quan st c kch thc dn n khng.

Khi , X l bin ngu nhin c phn phi Poisson vi tham s $\lambda = \mu t$. Ta c th xem $\lambda$ l trung bnh s ln s kin xy ra trong khong thi gian (khng gian) .

nh l $\,\,$ Nu $X$ l bin ngu nhin c phn phi Poisson, $X \sim Poi(\lambda)$, th ta c $$ E(X) = Var(X) = \lambda. $$

V d 22 $\,\,$ S lng cn bo ln trung bnh trong thnh ph l 2 cn bo mi nm. Xc sut chnh xc 3 cn bo s b vo thnh ph trong nm ti l bao nhiu?

Phân phối đều (The uniform distribution)¶

  • Cho $X$ l mt bin ngu nhin lin tc. Ta ni $X$ c phn phi u trn $[a, b]$ nu hm mt ca $X$ c xc nh bi $$ f_X(x) = \begin{cases} (b-a)^{-1} & \text{nu $x \in [a, b]$}, \\ 0 & \text{nu $x \notin [a, b]$}. \end{cases} $$ $\qquad$ Khi , ta k hiu $X \sim U(a, b)$.

  • Nu $X \sim U(a, b)$ th ta c $E(X) = \displaystyle \frac{a+b}{2}$ v $Var(X) = \displaystyle \frac{(b-a)^2}{12}$.

Phân phối chuẩn (The normal distribution)¶

Phn phi chun (Normal distribution) l phn phi quan trng nht trong xc sut v thng k. Phn phi chun c nu ra bi mt ngi Anh gc Php tn l Abraham de Moivre (1733). Sau , Gauss, mt nh ton hc ngi c, dng phn phi chun nghin cu cc d liu v thin vn hc (1809) v do vy n cng c gi l phn phi Gauss.

$\hspace{5cm}$

  • Mt bin ngu nhin lin tc $X$ c gi l c phn phi chun nu hm mt ca n cho bi $$ f_X(x) = \frac{1}{\sqrt{2\pi}}e^{-\frac{(x-\mu)^2}{2\sigma^2}}, $$ $\qquad$ vi $\mu \in \mathbb{R}$ v $\sigma > 0$ l hai hng s cho trc. Khi , ta k hiu $X \sim N(\mu, \sigma^2)$.

  • Nu $X \sim N(\mu, \sigma^2)$ th ta c $E(X) = \mu$ v $Var(X) = \sigma^2$.

  • Hnh dng v v tr ca ng cong phn phi chun ( th ca hm pdf) ph thuc vo hai tham s $$ v $$.

$\hspace{2cm}$ $\hspace{1cm}$

$\hspace{5cm}$

Mt s tnh cht ca phn phi chun

  • K vng v trung v bng nhau

  • th ca hm mt xc sut c hnh chung, i xng qua ng thng $x= \mu$

  • Din tch phn pha di ng cong (trn trc honh) trong on $[\mu-\sigma, \mu+\sigma]$ c gi tr xp x $0,68$; trong on $[\mu-2\sigma, \mu+2\sigma]$ c gi tr xp x $0,95$; trong on $[\mu-3\sigma, \mu+3\sigma]$ c gi tr xp x $0,997$.

$\hspace{2cm}$

Ch :

  • Phn phi chun $N(0, 1)$ c gi l phn phi chun chun tc. Hm mt xc sut v hm phn phi xc sut tch ly ca phn phi chun chun tc cho bi $$ f(z) = \frac{1}{\sqrt{2\pi}}e^{-\frac{z^2}{2}} \quad \text{and} \quad \Phi(z) = \frac{1}{\sqrt{2\pi}}\int_{-\infty}^z e^{-\frac{t^2}{2}} dt. $$

  • Nu $X \sim N(\mu, \sigma^2)$ th $\displaystyle Z = \frac{X-\mu}{\sigma} \sim N(0, 1)$.

V d: $\,\,$ Cho bin ngu nhin $X$ c phn phi chun chun tc

  • Tnh $P(X \leq 1,35)$

  • Tnh $P(-1,37 \leq X \leq 1,68)$

Gii $$ P(X \leq 1,35) = \Phi(1,35) = \frac{1}{\sqrt{2\pi}}\int_{-\infty}^{1,35} e^{-x^2/2}dx = 0,91149 $$ $$ P(-1,37 \leq X \leq 1,68) = \Phi(1,68) - \Phi(-1,37) = 0,95352 - 0,08534 \approx 0,87 $$

Phân phối Chi-bình phương¶

Hm Gamma $\,\,$ Cho $\alpha > 0$. Ta nh ngha $$ \Gamma(\alpha) = \int_0^\infty x^{\alpha-1}e^{-x}dx $$ Hm $\Gamma$ c cc tnh cht sau

  • Vi $\alpha > 1$ ta c $\Gamma(\alpha) = (\alpha-1)\Gamma(\alpha-1)$

  • Nu $n$ l mt s nguyn th $\Gamma(n) = n!$

  • $\Gamma(0,5) = \sqrt{\pi}$

Phn phi Chi-bnh phng

Cho $\nu$ l mt s nguyn dng. Mt bin ngu nhin lin tc $X$ c gi l c phn phi Chi-bnh phng vi tham s $\nu$ nu hm mt xc sut ca $X$ c dng $$ f_X(x) = \begin{cases} 0, & x < 0 \\ \frac{1}{2^{\nu/2}\Gamma(\nu/2)}x^{\nu/2-1}e^{-x/2}, & x \geq 0. \end{cases} $$ Khi ta k hiu $X \sim \chi^2(\nu)$. Tham s $\nu$ c gi l bc t do ca $X$.

Mnh

Nu cc bin ngu nhin $X_i N(0; 1) \,\, (1 i n)$ c lp th bin ngu nhin $$ Y = X^2_1 + X^2_2 + + X_n^2 $$ c phn phi chi-bnh phng vi bc t do l $n$.

Phân phối Student¶

Cho $X$ l mt bin ngu nhin lin tc. Nu hm mt ca $X$ c dng $$ f(x) = \frac{\Gamma(\frac{n+1}{2})}{\sqrt{n\pi}.\Gamma(\frac{n}{2})}\Big(1 + \frac{x^2}{n}\Big)^{-\frac{n+1}{2}} $$ vi $n > 0$ l mt s nguyn, th ta ni $X$ c phn phi student vi $n-1$ bc t do. K hiu $$ X \sim \frac{N(0,1)}{\sqrt{\chi^2_n/n}}. $$

Phn phi Student s c dng trong vic c lng khong ca trung bnh trong chng 5.

Phân phối Fisher (F-distribution)¶

Cho hai bin ngu nhin c lp $X$ v $Y$ c phn phi $\chi^2$ vi cc tham s ln lt l $\nu_1$ v $\nu_2$. Khi bin ngu nhin $$ Z = \frac{X/\nu_1}{Y/\nu_2} $$ c gi l c phn phi Fisher vi $\nu_1, \nu_2$ bc t do.

Hàm đặc trưng¶

nh ngha: $\,\,$ Cho $X$ l mt bin ngu nhin. Hm c trng ca $X$ l hm $\phi_X : \mathbb{R} \to \mathbb{C}$ c xc nh bi

  • Nu $X$ l ri rc vi cc gi tr l $x_1, x_2, \ldots$ th $$ \phi_X(t) = \sum_{k \geq 1}e^{ix_kt}P(X = x_k) $$
  • Nu $X$ l lin tc vi hm mt xc sut l $f(x)$ th $$ \phi_X(t) = \int_{-\infty}^\infty e^{ixt}f(x)dx $$ Lu rng $e^{ixt} = \cos(xt) + i\sin(xt)$ v $i^2 = -1$.
